- pyttsx3: For text-to-speech conversion
- speech_recognition: For capturing and converting voice to text
- wikipedia: To fetch summarized information from Wikipedia
- requests: For API calls to Gemini model
- psutil: For accessing system-level information and process handling
- subprocess & os: For executing and managing applications
- datetime & time: For handling current time and timestamps
- json: For saving and loading command history
- platform: For fetching OS details
- smtplib: Email sending capabilities (future extension)
- webbrowser: To open websites in the browser
